{"tid":2260313,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GFRIEND自曝全員吃貨！6人每月伙食費達1200萬","createTime":"2020-10-27T13:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T07:55:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"befd0ff32e7176fccc94221137ea55f6915382e0","tid":2260313,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:10:59.000Z","msg":"南韓女團GFriend由所願、睿隣、銀河、裕株、信飛、嚴智6人組成，以超強舞蹈實力走紅，是「2倍速舞」的始祖，近日正在認真準備月底線上演唱會和下月初新專輯中的6位成員也抽空接受台灣媒體越洋訪問，下半年回歸一改清純少女樣貌，「登大人」大走性感魅惑風的她們說，其實也一直在找代表自己個性的主題和風格，至於成熟路線，其他成員也一致認為隊長所願最適合。<br />\n<br />\n而整團都超會吃的GFRIEND一個月的伙食費竟高達1200萬韓幣（約35萬台幣），對此，她們也表示「就是要這樣吃，才有體力在舞台上帶給大家更精采的表演」，並透露6姝最喜歡的就是吃肉，近日更是迷上在家做飯，只要一有時間就會聚在一起煮一些簡單的料理來吃，主要是湯纇和煎餅，當然有時候也會點外送，更說疫情結束後，除了與各地的粉絲見面外，也很想要去旅行，享用當地特色美食，三句離不開吃，吃貨本性表露無遺。<br />\n<br />\n這次的線上演唱會正好是在萬聖節當天舉行，被問及印象深刻的過節經驗，成員們皆表示：「比起萬聖節的記憶，最近在主打歌〈APPLE〉中，每個人都有各自做了魔女角色的裝扮，讓我覺得印象很深刻，變成黑天鵝、賈方（阿拉丁中反派）、黑魔女等作品中的魔女，一起跳了舞，大家都覺得我們很適合吧？」<br />\n<br />\n最後，GFRIEND也不忘對台粉隔空喊話，表示謝謝大家的喜愛與支持，遠在南韓的6人也都非常想念台灣BUDDY們，並貼心說「現在大家都經歷著困難的時期，但相信很快就會好起來，你們也要照顧好自己，請一定要健康安全地等到我們可以見面的時候唷，希望能趕快見到大家」，也稱無法直接跟BUDDY們面對面相見感到非常遺憾，不過至少能用線上的方式跟大家相見，絕對會更認真的準備來報答各位粉絲。<br />\n<br />\nGFRIEND線上演唱會「2020 GFRIEND ONLINE CONCERT GFRIEND C<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />N」將於10月31日南韓時間下午5點在官方APP「WEVERSE」上進行直播，票券已於「Weverse Shop」開賣，官方會員可以韓幣29,000購買票券，一般票券售價為韓幣39,000，更多詳情請上WEVERSE查詢。"},{"pid":"e92b0f41d1fe7e0907dac88b274bbaaa572266ab","tid":2260313,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/26/2847489-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F26%2F2847489-PH.jpg&h=183dd6ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND一個月的伙食費竟高達1200萬韓幣。（圖／iME提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/26/2847490-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F26%2F2847490-PH.jpg&h=f8d5a420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND在主打歌〈APPLE〉中，都扮演了魔女。（圖／iME提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/26/2847491-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F26%2F2847491-PH.jpg&h=395b7be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GFRIEND將在本周六（31日）舉辦線上演唱會。（圖／iME提供）"},{"pid":"9d2745b79ca20d894e100fc45aa061e625da6cdb","tid":2260313,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WusGj0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWusGj0f.png&h=9fe9b033&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1HfprW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1HfprW.jpg&h=284adca1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xAWTa6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAWTa6Y.jpg&h=4570725b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hWjQ60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hWjQ60.jpg&h=26f2c885&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1xG7Z0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1xG7Z0n.jpg&h=835cdac9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nE0HOTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnE0HOTT.jpg&h=5b9b330c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06f150e0f0c27d71e275b99057a9cc83b78e5928","tid":2260313,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"咁大食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a9b64d73fa670b852377a59c9ef35187915877","tid":2260313,"uid":313222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"其他方面都好大食<img src=\